	   <tr><td colspan=2>The grizzly bear skin is used only for the Leatherfoot Raider's cap quest.<br><br>I've found two different items that are both named &quot;Grizzly Bear Skin.&quot;&nbsp;&nbsp;One is stackable, the other is not.<br><br>When you turn the skin in with other items for the quest, make sure you have an unstackable one.  The stackable one will not work.<br><br>Found this out the hard way.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
